Proposal to make crypto index synthetic coin.
Synthetic coin or coins similar to S&P 500 index fund. Suggestions for tradeble indexes:
  a) Basket of the major cryptocurrencyes, pegged to larger market capitalization cryptocurrencies.
  b) Basket of the all cryptocurrencyes listed on coinmarcetcap.com
  c) Basket of the all cryptocurrencyes whitelisted tokens on polkaswap.io DEX
  d) Basket of tokens with particular usecase (NFT platforms, Defi etc.)
  
  The goal: 
    a) To have a token with broad market eposure to build diversified portfolio .
    b) To have ability to build portfolio to loved ones, who dont have time or knoledge to build portfolio for themselves.
  Best would be a LP token with automatic compunding function, it would make it best DCA token with least effort to manage.
